name: New*
description:
PERSONALLY CUSTOMISED SILK SCREEN PRINT
Edition: 70
Size: 20"x26"
Stock: 130m Ivory 2R55
Colours: 1 colour: PMS7424u (Pink) + Hand Emboss

When you purchase your New* artwork you have the opportunity to select your very own hand embossed 'fine-print' for the poster.

The poster is printed with a large starburst containing the headline to the work: New*. The asterisk (from the headline*) is reprinted at the bottom of the page, but the conditions or 'fine-print' for the poster have been left blank.

With each order you can select your own terms and conditions for the work. When you select your 'fine-print', it will be hand embossed, character by character by A Curly One, producing a 1 off original, brand NEW ready to ship your way.

All fine-print will be stamped in UPPERCASE and you can choose one phrase from the following options:

*FOR A LIMITED TIME ONLY
*CONDITIONS APPLY
*WHILE STOCKS LAST

All artwork is signed by the artist, 'bob' from A Curly One and embossed with the number of the screen printed edition.

***Notes about to select which one when do a test
